scoringPlays.text: Tra Minter 8 Yd Run (Gavin Patterson Kick)
Kawaan Baker 3 Yd Run (Gavin Patterson Kick), (G. Patterson KICK)
Tyrek Allen 75 Yd pass from KHA'Darris Davis (Hunter Hanson Kick)
Evan Orth 19 Yd Run (Gavin Patterson Kick)
Jordan McCray 9 Yd pass from Evan Orth (Gavin Patterson Kick)
Tra Minter 75 Yd Punt Return (Gavin Patterson Kick)
Jahmmir Taylor 56 Yd pass from Cephus Johnson (Gavin Patterson Kick)

videos.headline: South Alabama strikes first with 8-yard TD run
videos.description: RB Tra Minter somehow stays on his feet and gets himself across the goal line, giving the Jaguars an early 7-0 lead.

videos.headline: South Alabama doubles lead on 3-yard jet sweep
videos.description: WR Kawaan Baker takes the hand off and gets the edge, scoring easily to make it 14-0 Jaguars.

videos.headline: Alabama State explodes for 75-yard TD pass
videos.description: QB KHA'Darris Davis unloads a pass to WR Tyrek Allen, who brings it down and outruns the defense, cutting the Jaguars' lead to 14-7.

videos.headline: South Alabama responds with 20-yard QB run
videos.description: QB Evan Orth keeps it himself and slips through tackles en route to the end zone, extending the Jaguars' lead to 21-7.

videos.headline: Jaguars widen lead with 14-yard TD pass
videos.description: QB Evan Orth throws a dime to WR Jordan McCray, who makes a leaping reception in the end zone to make it 28-7 South Alabama.

videos.headline: South Alabama pours it on with 56-yard TD pass
videos.description: Backup QB Cephus Johnson puts one on the money to WR Jahmmir Taylor, who gets to the end zone and makes it 45-7 Jaguars.
